 entirely in your browser via the Web Audio API. Supports MP3, WAV, M4A, OGG, and FLAC input; exports to WAV, MP3, or OGG. No upload, no sign-up, no install — a free alternative to Adobe Audition and Audacity Cloud.\"}]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"No Install, Any Device\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Runs entirely in your browser. Works on Windows, Mac, Linux, and Chromebooks — no 100 MB download for a 30-second trim.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trim, Cut & Export in Seconds\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drop an MP3 or WAV, drag to select the part you want, hit trim, and download. Most edits take under a minute.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Convert MP3, WAV, OGG & More\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Import MP3, WAV, OGG, AAC, FLAC, or WebM. Export as WAV (lossless), MP3, or OGG with configurable bitrate.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Your Files Stay Private\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"All processing happens locally using the Web Audio API. Nothing is uploaded — your audio never leaves your device.\"}]]}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2a\",null,{}]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L16\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-16 space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trim Audio Online — No Install Required\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"You shouldn't need to download a 100 MB desktop app just to trim an MP3 or cut a section from a WAV file. Free Tool Shed's Audio Editor lets you trim audio online, convert between formats, and apply effects — all in your browser. No installation, no account, no subscription. It works on any device: Windows, Mac, Linux, Chromebooks, even a locked-down work computer.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Unlike Adobe Audition ($22.99/month) or Audacity (desktop-only), this tool is built for quick edits: drop a file, make your cut, download the result. Most tasks take under a minute. Need more? Apply fade in/out, normalize volume, reduce noise, reverse audio, or convert WAV to MP3 — all processed locally. Your files never leave your device.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Visual waveform display with per-pixel peak rendering\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Click-and-drag region selection on the waveform\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Trim (crop) audio to selection\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Delete selected region and join remaining parts\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Silence selected region\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Fade in and fade out effects\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Normalize volume to peak amplitude\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Reverse audio (entire track or selection)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Amplify with configurable gain factor\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Noise reduction with adjustable strength\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"50-step undo/redo history\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Export as WAV (lossless), MP3, or OGG\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Configurable bitrate for compressed formats\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ctrl+scroll to zoom toward cursor, scroll to pan\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Keyboard shortcuts (Space, Delete, T, Ctrl+Z/Y)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Time grid overlay with automatic scaling\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Real-time playhead animation during playback\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Selection-only playback preview\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Mute toggle and gain control\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Drag-and-drop file import\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Supports MP3, WAV, OGG, AAC, FLAC, and WebM input\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Export preferences saved across sessions\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Client-side only — audio never leaves your browser\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"How to Trim Audio Online (5 Steps)\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"1. Import your audio file\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"1. Import your audio file\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drag and drop an audio file onto the editor, or click to browse. Supported formats include MP3, WAV, OGG, AAC, FLAC, and WebM. Your file is decoded l