unning entirely in your browser via the Web Audio API. Supports MP3, WAV, M4A, OGG, and FLAC input; exports to WAV, MP3, or OGG. No upload, no sign-up, no install — a free alternative to Adobe Audition and Audacity Cloud.\"}]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"No Install, Any Device\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Runs entirely in your browser. Works on Windows, Mac, Linux, and Chromebooks — no 100 MB download for a 30-second trim.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trim, Cut & Export in Seconds\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drop an MP3 or WAV, drag to select the part you want, hit trim, and download. Most edits take under a minute.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Convert MP3, WAV, OGG & More\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Import MP3, WAV, OGG, AAC, FLAC, or WebM. Export as WAV (lossless), MP3, or OGG with configurable bitrate.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Your Files Stay Private\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"All processing happens locally using the Web Audio API. Nothing is uploaded — your audio never leaves your device.\"}]]}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2a\",null,{}]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L16\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-16 space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trim Audio Online — No Install Required\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"You shouldn't need to download a 100 MB desktop app just to trim an MP3 or cut a section from a WAV file. Free Tool Shed's Audio Editor lets you trim audio online, convert between formats, and apply effects — all in your browser. No installation, no account, no subscription. It works on any device: Windows, Mac, Linux, Chromebooks, even a locked-down work computer.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Unlike Adobe Audition ($22.99/month) or Audacity (desktop-only), this tool is built for quick edits: drop a file, make your cut, download the result. Most tasks take under a minute. Need more? Apply fade in/out, normalize volume, reduce noise, reverse audio, or convert WAV to MP3 — all processed locally. Your files never leave your device.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Visual waveform display with per-pixel peak rendering\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Click-and-drag region selection on the waveform\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Trim (crop) audio to selection\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Delete selected region and join remaining parts\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Silence selected region\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Fade in and fade out effects\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Normalize volume to peak amplitude\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Reverse audio (entire track or selection)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Amplify with configurable gain factor\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Noise reduction with adjustable strength\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"50-step undo/redo history\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Export as WAV (lossless), MP3, or OGG\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Configurable bitrate for compressed formats\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ctrl+scroll to zoom toward cursor, scroll to pan\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Keyboard shortcuts (Space, Delete, T, Ctrl+Z/Y)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Time grid overlay with automatic scaling\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Real-time playhead animation during playback\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Selection-only playback preview\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Mute toggle and gain control\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Drag-and-drop file import\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Supports MP3, WAV, OGG, AAC, FLAC, and WebM input\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Export preferences saved across sessions\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Client-side only — audio never leaves your browser\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"How to Trim Audio Online (5 Steps)\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"1. Import your audio file\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"1. Import your audio file\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drag and drop an audio file onto the editor, or click to browse. Supported formats include MP3, WAV, OGG, AAC, FLAC, and WebM. Your file is decoded locally in your browser — nothing is uploaded.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"2. Navigate the waveform\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"2. Navigate the waveform\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Use the visual waveform to see your audio. Hold Ctrl (or Cmd on Mac) and scroll to zoom in and out — the view zooms toward your cursor for fast navigation. Scroll without a modifier to pan left and right. Click anywhere to position the playhead, then press Space to play.\"}]]}],\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\",\"$L2e\"]}]]}],\"$L2f\",\"$L30\",\"$L31\"]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/04v8-.addjpun.js\",\"async\":true,\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n23:[\"$\",\"$L32\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$28\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@33\"}]}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"li\",\"3. Select a region\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"3. Select a region\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Click and drag on the waveform to highlight a region. The selection is shown in green. Use selection-only playback to preview exactly what you've selected before making edits.\"}]]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"li\",\"4. Edit and apply effects\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"4. Edit and apply effects\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Use the toolbar buttons to trim, delete, or silence the selection. Apply effects like fade in, fade out, normalize, reverse, amplify, or noise reduction from the effects bar below the waveform.\"}]]}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"li\",\"5. Export your edited audio\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"5. Export your edited audio\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Choose your export format (WAV for lossless, MP3 or OGG for compressed) and bitrate, then click Download. The file is encoded in your browser and saved directly to your device.\"}]]}]\n2f:[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Audio Editor\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Match sample rate to the source\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Match sample rate to the source\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Resampling audio (44.1 kHz → 48 kHz, for instance) introduces interpolation artifacts. Export at the same sample rate as your source unless you specifically need to change it.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Normalize before, not after, hard edits\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2f:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Normalize before, not after, hard edits\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Normalizing first gives you a consistent peak level to cut against. Doing it after a hard cut can re-amplify clipping that the cut would have removed.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Use short fades to hide hard cuts\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2f:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Use short fades to hide hard cuts\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Even a 20–50 ms fade in/out smooths the click that abrupt edits create. The tool's fade controls are deliberately small-default for exactly this case.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Keep an unmodified original\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2f:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Keep an unmodified original\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Edits are destructive in any waveform editor. Export a copy of the trimmed/cleaned version under a new filename rather than overwriting the source.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labe