, OGG, and FLAC input; exports to WAV, MP3, or OGG. No upload, no sign-up, no install — a free alternative to Adobe Audition and Audacity Cloud.\"}]}]\n9:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"No Install, Any Device\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Runs entirely in your browser. Works on Windows, Mac, Linux, and Chromebooks — no 100 MB download for a 30-second trim.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trim, Cut & Export in Seconds\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drop an MP3 or WAV, drag to select the part you want, hit trim, and download. Most edits take under a minute.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Convert MP3, WAV, OGG & More\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Import MP3, WAV, OGG, AAC, FLAC, or WebM. Export as WAV (lossless), MP3, or OGG with configurable bitrate.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Your Files Stay Private\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"All processing happens locally using the Web Audio API. Nothing is uploaded — your audio never leaves your device.\"}]]}]]}]\na:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{}]}]\nb:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"classNam